article.linkText: Toppin scores 25, New Mexico downs Air Force 85-66
article.story: COLORADO SPRINGS, Colo. -- — JT Toppin had 25 points in New Mexico's 85-66 win over Air Force on Saturday night. Toppin had 13 rebounds for the Lobos (16-3, 4-2 Mountain West Conference). Jamal Mashburn Jr. scored 13 points, going 4 of 11 from the floor, including 1 for 6 from 3-point range, and 4 for 5 from the line. Beau Becker led the way for the Falcons (7-10, 0-5) with 23 points and six assists. Rytis Petraitis added 18 points and two steals for Air Force ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
